---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout-en.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Services – AI Transformation and Paid Social | Adorable"
	description="Adorable offers AI consulting for companies wanting to implement AI, and Paid Social for digital advertising on Meta, LinkedIn, TikTok and more."
	swedishPath="/tjanster"
>
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="hero-title">Services</h1>
				<p class="hero-intro">
					I help companies grow – either by implementing AI in their operations, 
					or by driving results with digital advertising. Sometimes both at once.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="services">
					<div class="service-card">
						<h2>AI Transformation</h2>
						<p class="service-tagline">For companies that want to start using AI for real</p>
						
						<p>AI is no longer future talk – it's a tool that can make your business more efficient today. But where do you start? And how do you avoid the most common pitfalls?</p>
						
						<h3>What I help with:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Workshops and training</strong> – Give the team knowledge and confidence to use AI</li>
							<li><strong>AI strategy</strong> – Identify where AI creates the most value in your specific business</li>
							<li><strong>Implementation</strong> – Help getting started with the right tools and processes</li>
							<li><strong>AI policy</strong> – Framework for safe and responsible AI use</li>
						</ul>

						<h3>Industries I work with:</h3>
						<p>Education, construction and other industries where AI can make a concrete difference. Both B2B and B2C.</p>
						
						<a href="/en/ai" class="cta-link">Read more about AI consulting →</a>
					</div>

					<div class="service-card">
						<h2>Paid Social</h2>
						<p class="service-tagline">Digital advertising that drives results</p>
						
						<p>Paid social is more than "running some ads on Facebook". It's about understanding the platforms, the audience and how to build campaigns that actually convert.</p>
						
						<h3>Platforms:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Meta</strong> – Facebook and Instagram</li>
							<li><strong>LinkedIn</strong> – For B2B and recruitment</li>
							<li><strong>TikTok</strong> – For younger audiences and viral reach</li>
							<li><strong>YouTube</strong> – Video advertising with precision</li>
							<li><strong>Pinterest</strong> – Inspiration and purchase intent</li>
							<li><strong>Snapchat</strong> – Younger audiences and AR experiences</li>
						</ul>

						<h3>What I help with:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Strategy</strong> – Right platforms, messaging and budget for your goals</li>
							<li><strong>Setup</strong> – Campaign structure, tracking and creative</li>
							<li><strong>Optimization</strong> – Ongoing improvement based on data</li>
							<li><strong>Training</strong> – Teach your team to handle advertising themselves</li>
						</ul>
						
						<a href="/en/paid-social" class="cta-link">Read more about Paid Social →</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section cta-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Not sure what you need?</h2>
				<p>Reach out and we'll have a conversation to figure it out together. No commitment.</p>
				<a href="/en/contact" class="cta-button">Contact me</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		background: #fff;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.hero .container {
		max-width: 900px;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: #000;
	}

	.hero-intro {
		font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #000;
	}

	.section {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
	}

	.services {
		display: grid;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.services {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 4rem;
		}
	}

	.service-card {
		padding: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.service-card h2 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
		color: #000;
	}

	.service-tagline {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
	}

	.service-card p {
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #333;
	}

	.service-card h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
		color: #000;
	}

	.service-card ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
	}

	.service-card li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #333;
	}

	.cta-link {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		color: #000;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
		padding-bottom: 2px;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}

	.cta-link:hover {
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		background: #fafafa;
		border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
	}

	.cta-section h2 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.cta-section p {
		color: #666;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
	}

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		background: #000;
		color: #fff;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		border-radius: 6px;
		transition: opacity 0.2s;
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		opacity: 0.85;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
		}

		.section {
			padding: 3rem 0;
		}

		.service-card {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
